&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Quality and Governance:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Establish and monitor data quality tests to ensure completeness, accuracy, and consistency. Partner with business stakeholders, IT, and data engineering teams to define and enforce governance standards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Accessibility and Democratization:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Develop intuitive, business-friendly data models and assets optimized for analytics. Ensure the right data is available to the right people at the right time, empowering self-service analytics and operational reporting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
