&lt;p&gt;Build and deliver frequent, customized training sessions and daily &quot;Selling Process Gems&quot; built on specific examples of Challenger behaviors applied to real MX prospect situations&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
